<DIV>So what if the charmed pets hit for 800, thats how hard the mob we are fighting hits, so it puts&nbsp;us on equal ground.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Currently there is no way to solo in OOW.&nbsp; Even with a slowed target and a hasted charmed pet, the charmed pet will always die first, and if charm breaks&nbsp;its an&nbsp;instant tell to the clerics.&nbsp;&nbsp; Chanters will never be able to solo again with this change.&nbsp; I would rather Sony make less mobs charmable (we can find them) and let the mob hit for what it should.</DIV>
