		<td rowspan=2 bgcolor="#050A0E" width=1><img src="/i/p.gif" height=1 width=1 border=0 alt=""><br></td>
	
		<td colspan=2 class="msg_text_cell" width="100%" valign=top style="text-align: justify; 
		" 
			>
			<DIV></DIV>
<DIV>
<P>------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------</P>
<P>CaptKanuck wrote:</P>
<P>I guess not much thought was put into the Cleric class. Thanks for nothing!</P>
<P>&nbsp;</P>
<P>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; First round...</P>
<P>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Focus on making classes more desirable for groups and raids...</P>
<P>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; I did not think clerics needed any additional group or raid desirabiliy...</P>
<P>-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------</P>
<P>the problem is boosting druids ability to replace clerics as healer reduces clerics grouping role without giving us somethign to offer (which druids have in spades) to compete.</P>
<P>one of the cleric top 10 list is a 2ndry role as our primary is being eroded away, supposedly this is being looked at for class balancing, BUT the 2 need doing together not 1 first then the other, if our primary role gets reduced (i.e druid +25% heals) we need some other benefit (i.e secondary role) so that we retain group desireabilty.</P>
<P>see this below comparison to see what effect this druid boost has :</P>
<P>-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------</P>
<P>Cleric Pious Light</P>
<P>3770 hp 740 mana : 5.09 hp/mana</P>
<P>Druid Chlorotorp</P>
<P>2420 hp 627 mana : 3.85 hp/mana</P>
<P>+25%</P>
<P>3025 hp 627 mana : 4.82 hp/mana</P>
<P>Its a lot closer now. 95% of the clerics efficiency.</P>
<P>--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------</P>
<P>No we dont suffer from group problems now, BUT we will if our primary isnt needed and we have no secondary which this change does.</P>
<P>IF the druid change goes through on april 6th clerics NEED the '2ndry role were looking at' implementing too or our group role will be near non existant!</P></DIV>	
		</td></tr>
